{
  "stem": "13395.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they took us out, marched us outside the town to dig trenches, that when the tanks roll in-- because we could already hear the-- we could hear already the guns, day and night.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew it's over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the planes were flying over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would herd us into one room, because they said that we would give them signals to bomb the factories.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, and you were always afraid that they will accuse you of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You always lived in fear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You lived in fear of the men who would, who would beat you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see, women had different experiences in camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Women were beaten by men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Women were afraid to be raped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Women were in camp, the young married women, mothers, the children were torn away from them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there they saw German children walking with their families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Women had been put to work in places where men couldn't work, that it was too difficult for men.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a very different experience to be a woman prisoner than it was a man prisoner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm not minimizing the men's experiences, but there was a difference.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were taken to dig the, the trenches so then the tanks come that they should at least hold them back, because, of course, the Germans didn't even have anything anymore to keep them back.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were working, and it was already May.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was raining.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we only have that one coat, and it's soaked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there is no where to dry the wet clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You put it on in the morning again, as you took it off in the evening.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
